Typical predicon, shoddy workmanship, limbs always poppin off.

{Grimlock}

    Grimlock grumbles watching the head roll off down the hill then looking
down at the rest of the pred, "Me Grimlock need new strategy." Leaning down
the dinobot takes Infernos body in his jaws and turns to head for Maximal
base leaving the head where ever it fell, forgetting about it pretty much as
soon as it's out of sight...
